cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.DB, cs.IR. 

The paper proposes a new algorithm for knowledge base completion using reinforcement learning, which falls under the sub-fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The algorithm also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and database systems (cs.DB) as it deals with answering questions and navigating a knowledge graph. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the algorithm involves finding predictive paths between entities in the knowledge base.
